1330.name: Ni(-)
1330.Applications: Joining and cladding grey and malleable cast iron, also suitable for joint welds between steel , copper and copper alloys, especially for maintenance and repair.
1330.Suitable_For: Grey cast iron, Malleable cast iron, EN 1561: EN-GJL-100 (GG10) till EN-GJL-350 (GG35), EN 1562: EN-GJMB-350 (GTS 35) till EN-GJMB-550 (GTS 55), EN- GJMW-350 (GTW 35) till EN- GJMW-550 (GTW 55).
